Module io.jstach.rainbowgum

Package io.jstach.rainbowgum

@NonNullByDefault({PARAMETER,RETURN_TYPE,FIELD,TYPE_BOUND,TYPE_ARGUMENT,ARRAY_CONTENTS}) package io.jstach.rainbowgum
RainbowGum core components. The flow of log messages is as follows:
  1. RainbowGum
  2. LogRouter
  3. LogPublisher
  4. LogAppender
  5. LogEncoder
  6. LogOutput
